THOTH_ATLAS_ART 1
# Reviewable authored pixel atlas source.
# Each sprite block is 16 rows of 16 glyphs. "." leaves the generated base pixel unchanged.
# Palette roles:
# o/x outline and void, n/N/m/M/h neutral metal, g/G grass, d/D dirt,
# z/Z sand, l/L snow, j/J mud, w/W water, t/T leaves, b/B wood, s/S stone, i/I iron,
# c/C copper, k/K coal, f/F floor, y/Y belts, r/R heat,
# e/E electric blue, p/P lab purple, q/Q glass glow, u/U skin, v/V player suit.

